results.name: Shifts left by 3 places under series reversion.
comment: Series reversion of the g.f. gives the same sequence with three initial terms (1, 1, 1) dropped.
formula: G.f. satisfies A((A(x) - x - x^2 - x^3)/x^3) = x.
mathematica: Nest[InverseSeries[#] x^3 + x^3 + x^2 + x &, x + O[x]^2, 10][[3]]
results.author: _Vladimir Reshetnikov_, Aug 08 2019
